						<span class="tags">Tagged with <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/fiat-money/" rel="tag">fiat money</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/mises/" rel="tag">Mises</a></span>					</p>
				</div>

