						<span class="categories">Filed under <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/category/banks/" rel="category tag">Banks</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/category/fiat-currency/" rel="category tag">Fiat currency</a></span>
											</p>
