						<span class="categories">Filed under <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/category/euro/" rel="category tag">Euro</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/category/europe/" rel="category tag">Europe</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/category/fiat-currency/" rel="category tag">Fiat currency</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/category/france-2/" rel="category tag">France</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/category/germany-2/" rel="category tag">Germany</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/category/spain/" rel="category tag">Spain</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/category/uncategorized/" rel="category tag">Uncategorized</a></span>
