						<span class="tags">Tagged with <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/currency-war/" rel="tag">currency war</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/dollar-2/" rel="tag">dollar</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/fiat-currency-2/" rel="tag">fiat currency</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/international-monetary-fund/" rel="tag">International Monetary Fund</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/united-states/" rel="tag">United States</a></span>					</p>
