						<span class="categories">Filed under <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/category/fed/" rel="category tag">FED</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/category/fiat-currency/" rel="category tag">Fiat currency</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/category/history/" rel="category tag">History</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/category/inflation/" rel="category tag">Inflation</a></span>
						<span class="tags">Tagged with <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/financial-repression/" rel="tag">Financial Repression</a></span>					</p>
