					<div class="post-info">
						<p>
							<span class="time">March 28, 2012</span>
															<span class="author">by <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/author/mktgeistmike/" title="Posts by mktgeistmike" rel="author">mktgeistmike</a></span>
																						<span class="post-comments"><a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/2012/03/28/under-which-conditions-will-fed-money-printing-create-high-inflation/#respond" title="Comment on Under Which Conditions Will Fed Money Printing Create High&nbsp;Inflation?">Leave a comment</a></span>
